g.text: Proportion of unpaid domestic and care work done by males
When including all countries, relationship between male share of domestic and care work and fertility is negative.
Confounding effect of economic and educational opportunities for women and girls has not been controlled for.
Gender share of unpaid domestic work and fertility rate
Time use data from the UN SDGs database; total fertility rate from the UN World Population Prospects. Analysis by freerangestats.info.
